{"tid":1975701,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方獲搜令查「周庭FB訂閱者資料」，周庭：Facebook拒絕交出","createTime":"2020-04-16T17:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T19:10:36.000Z","uid":166601,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce56d2874e04416a0b0d4328f5993db1e30afab","tid":1975701,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"警方去年就6月21日「包圍警總」事件，以煽惑罪拘捕黃之鋒、 周庭等香港眾志成員。審判之中，黃之鋒與周庭獲控方告知，警察早於去年9月起以「搜查警總」名義，取得法庭手令，檢查兩人存放於警總內手機&mdash;&mdash;即黃之鋒的iPhone XR和周庭的Google Pixel。另外，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">警方更取得手令，到Facebook總部查閱周庭專頁的訂閱者資料，包括IP地址、用戶登記資料等有關紀錄。</span></strong>黃之鋒和周庭昨（15）日向高等法院申請司法覆核，要求裁定三名裁判官簽發的手令與警方執行手令均屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n周庭於今（16）晚表示，Facebook香港辦公室員工聯絡了她，指因為「用戶資料都由美國的Facebook公司總部持有」，所以「Facebook香港辦公室拒絕警方要求，沒有交出任何資料」。<br />\n<br />\n汁：<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/133939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F133939&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10FGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=3412a9fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/133939</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知Facebook 會唔會有朝一日跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家點都好都一定要<strong>用VPN 同減少係網上公開個人資料</strong>"},{"pid":"ec549dd456d658e0d68097ee63d44f18e168c7ed","tid":1975701,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dad62ef97e5febfa6ed5efd6834b7529ded3a07","tid":1975701,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:09:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29eae3b759c36af12cc7f6f6260394883a8014fc","tid":1975701,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c784ee1c0573d1292558ec543f8e0bbbb0cf5a35","tid":1975701,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"開post前自己search下有無人開過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d23d00f3e925067e6dc647d991998eb8c5a27e","tid":1975701,"uid":166601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:09:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dcc4345158027f7e2811a7a3b9a01e03961f101","tid":1975701,"uid":166601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c784ee1c0573d1292558ec543f8e0bbbb0cf5a35","tid":1975701,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:09:32.000Z","msg":"開post前自己search下有無人開過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:10:46.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩熱門見唔到...<br />\n收皮先啦我都係"},{"pid":"156a2764fe24f574b0dd01606b500318ba3e31e4","tid":1975701,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8d3eea13cf87479193f07c6b889c6350ef704d","tid":1975701,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T19:10:36.000Z","msg":"HK FB is doing the right thing deferring that to USA Headquarter."}]}